hands_on_practices.solution:
我们有沿 x 轴的运动，
$$v(t)=\alpha t\,,\qquad \alpha t<c\,,\qquad \gamma(t)=\frac1{\sqrt{1-\frac{v^2}{c^2}}}
=\bigl(1-\tfrac{\alpha^2t^2}{c^2}\bigr)^{-1/2}\,. $$
四维速度的分量为
$$U^0=\gamma c,\quad U^1=\gamma v=\gamma\alpha t\,. $$
固有时导数与坐标时导数的关系为 $d/d\tau=\gamma\,d/dt$。因此
$$\frac{dU^0}{dt}
=c\frac{d\gamma}{dt}
=c\;\frac12(1-\tfrac{\alpha^2t^2}{c^2})^{-3/2}\cdot\frac{2\alpha^2t}{c^2}
=\frac{\alpha^2t}{c}\,\gamma^3,$$
$$\frac{dU^1}{dt}
=\frac{d}{dt}(\gamma v)
=\gamma\,\alpha+v\,\frac{d\gamma}{dt}
=\gamma\alpha+\alpha t\;\frac{\alpha^2t}{c^2}\gamma^3
=\alpha\gamma^3\,. $$
于是四维力 $K^\mu=m\,dU^\mu/d\tau=m\gamma\,dU^\mu/dt$ 的分量为
$$K^0=m\gamma\frac{\alpha^2t}{c}\,\gamma^3
=m\frac{\alpha^2t}{c}\,\gamma^4,\qquad
K^1=m\gamma\alpha\gamma^3
=m\alpha\,\gamma^4. $$
其不变量模长为
$$|K|=\sqrt{-(K_\mu K^\mu)}=\sqrt{(K^1)^2-(K^0)^2}
=m\alpha\,\gamma^4\sqrt{1-\frac{\alpha^2t^2}{c^2}}
=m\alpha\,\gamma^3
=m\alpha\Bigl(1-\frac{\alpha^2t^2}{c^2}\Bigr)^{-3/2}\,. $$
